@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_yidmxd(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.abs(((v2 + 0.12 + v0 + 0.84) / (v0 + 0.28 / v0 + 0.21)))
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.abs(0.33))
    v0 = v1
    tmp = wp.sin((tmp + (v1 + 0.45 - v0 + 0.99)))
    data[tid] = v0
